Class FetchAddressService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.String,java.lang.Void,java.util.List<android.location.Address>>
      • com.example.android.FetchAddressService

  • public class FetchAddressService
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.String,java.lang.Void,java.util.List<android.location.Address>>
    A place-to-coordinates translation class. It can retrieve an Address from a LatLng, or a group of Address from a location name. This class is intended to aid SelectTripActivity in addresses translation.
